  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p><strong>Beginners skiing in Breckenridge</strong></p>
<p>Breckenridge’s ski school is renowned for its excellent teaching and you will soon be able to conquer the plentiful, well-groomed, gentle slopes of peaks 8 and 9.</p>
<p><strong>Intermediates skiing in Breckenridge</strong></p>
<p>Mile after mile of suitable runs through beautiful scenery, from open bowls to tree lined trails. The testing descents of Peak 10 will provide a steeper challenge.</p>
<p><strong>Advanced skiing in Breckenridge</strong></p>
<p>Over 400 acres of uninterrupted powder, huge mogul fields, glade skiing and open bowls ensure a new challenge each day.</p>
<p><strong>Snowboarding in Breckenridge</strong></p>
<p>A legendary snowboarding mecca with a first class dedicated park, great natural terrain and special clinics for all levels of boarder.</p>]]></generalInformation>
